"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721c8d7bf22c51cc4adccd62f3ff5bdd91e440aa","tid":216481,"uid":56716,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:42:36.000Z","msg":"佢衰在蠢，貪錢就有保留，移情別戀處理感情手法極差比帽人戴就真。佢同李泳豪一齊咁多年，要貪錢一早貪咗，以佢港姐名銜加上樣又唔錯又大波，一定大把有錢佬肯包佢，同埋佢同吳帥好似已經識咗好多年，入行前已經識，理應不是貪錢，空心老棺呢啲都係報紙講，可能楊一早知佢唔係有錢人。佢衰在未同李泳豪分手就同第二個一齊仲搞大個肚，同吳帥分手仲要夾硬生個b出嚟，佢唔生都可能搵到人埋單，生咗咁就一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84816a318930bf1b57e903fe085e3c1d25a76489","tid":216481,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>盲腸<br />\n你地唔覺得佢反而係最有資格代表香港小姐咩？<br />\n細個做ptgf,大個做香港小姐👍</blockquote><br />\n咪臭係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港小姐好矜貴咩"},{"pid":"148f101fc0c3cddb0b56b363d7d0bdce0c04b12f","tid":216481,"uid":16250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:06:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾d風度<br />\n佢已經好慘<br />\n上錯賊船<br />\n而家獨力養女<br />\n你仲要踩佢一腳<br />\n<br />\n佢已經得到好大嘅懲罰</blockquote><br />\n口德+10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw屌你老母（口德-10）"},{"pid":"af5a3821bfa29ad46f1b221edaf9ddf456dc36b4","tid":216481,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:07:54.000Z","msg":"佢真係好鈍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8b52d76221cbe1333f4ca07751a4bd7284878a","tid":216481,"uid":32051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:10:21.000Z","msg":"係咪貪錢真係唔知，但派帽賤過雞就一定真。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條路都係自己揀，依家返大陸陪老細應該都好搵，大把方法搵錢，洗撚擔心佢咩。"},{"pid":"8ec1d9108a1132ca9f591dcf39f9d394e4dec6e4","tid":216481,"uid":39431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:47:26.000Z","msg":"<span sty